original_client_text.markup_text:
12 DAYS OF CHRISTMAS RECIPES🎄

Day 9: Maple pumpkin, pistachio and quinoa salad

Packed with loads of delicious flavours and textures, this salad is the perfect vegetarian side dish you need to make for your Christmas Day feast! 🤤

Ingredients:

A large handful of baby spinach
1/2 a red onion, finely sliced
1 avocado, diced
1/3 cup sun dried tomatoes
1/3 cup pistachios, chopped
100g feta

MAPLE ROASTED PUMPKIN:
600g pumpkin, diced
Drizzle of olive oil
Drizzle of maple syrup
Salt
— bake at 200°c for 30-35 minutes

QUNIOA:
1 cup quinoa
2 cups vegetable stock
— cook as per directions

DRESSING:
Juice of 1 lemon
2tbsp olive oil
1tsp minced garlic
Salt/pepper

#sidesalad #sidedish #sidedishrecipe #saladlover #saladrecipes #saladrecipe #summersalad
